{"tid":2495525,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北京斥人權問題上日美對中國和世界人民有欠帳","createTime":"2021-04-19T08:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T09:15:56.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8c0bd8d7914a569078b0f27f23b2f9aa0b8b8b73","tid":2495525,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:33:24.000Z","msg":"在北京，外交部發言人汪文斌回應美日領導會晤並發表聯合聲明的涉華內容，表示世界上只有以聯合國為核心的國際體系，和以聯合國憲章為基礎的國際關係基本準則。美日代表不了國際社會，沒有資格定義國際秩序，更沒有資格將自身的標準強加於人。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，在人權問題上，日美對中國人民和世界人民是有欠帳的。日本上世紀30年代發動的侵略戰爭給亞洲國家特別是中國人民造成了深重的災難。美國長期推行窮兵黷武政策。他認為，日美應該切實反省並糾正侵略行徑和侵犯他國人權的錯誤行為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586554-20210419.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586554-20210419.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx4DkkQuUBcdRTUhzZaMUkok%3D&h=6f125318\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586554-20210419.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=96724ce1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586554-20210419.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"693d59185d868501877a3beffde5d6f90abf51a0","tid":2495525,"uid":362754,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:35:07.000Z","msg":"世界第二大經濟體又想扮受害者？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b838d89918db30bd99e32b9e3eb76f94deb437","tid":2495525,"uid":287107,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:36:34.000Z","msg":"坐睇其他國家講元朝打到成個歐亞支那對全世界有欠帳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20a3b483f7b20bc5d1d650570a8da876270fefa","tid":2495525,"uid":83713,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:36:42.000Z","msg":"人權關你班支那豚撚事？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://zhoubao.minghui.org/mh/haizb/media/files/2007/08/zxtup-07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https